### Step 1d: Test Suite 4 — `PATCH /api/cards/:id/move` (card move with broadcast)

```javascript
describe('PATCH /api/cards/:id/move', () => {
  let server, baseUrl, wsUrl, cardId;

  before(async () => {
    initDb(':memory:');
    const card = createCard({ title: 'Move Me', column: 'ready' });
